Module com.example.miniproject2

Class Board

java.lang.Object
com.example.miniproject2.model.ABoard
com.example.miniproject2.model.Board
All Implemented Interfaces:
IBoard
public class Board extends ABoard
The Board class represents the game board for the Sudoku puzzle. It initializes a 6x6 grid and provides methods for filling the board with valid numbers according to Sudoku rules.
